        "purpose": "english_translation",
        "value": "Provisional Junior Councillors (gon-shō-sanji) — the tail of Chōshū's named official roster, continued from the facing page (p204_R, which carries the ○山口藩 marker and the senior officials 知事・大参事・権大参事・少参事). Eight names are listed here, beginning with Mōri Chikanobu."
